# Building

(Requires GNU Make 4+)

```shell
$ make terltris
```

# Running

```shell
$ ./terltris
```

# Installing

This is left as an exercise for the reader.

# Dependencies

Via your favorite package manager:
- [Erlang/OTP]
- [SDL 2]

Via [Erlang.mk]:
- [esdl2]

## On macOS:

```shell
$ brew install erlang sdl2 sdl2_image sdl2_ttf
```

[Homebrew]: https://brew.sh/
[Erlang/OTP]: https://github.com/erlang/otp
[SDL 2]: https://www.libsdl.org
[esdl2]: https://github.com/ninenines/esdl2
[Erlang.mk]: https://erlang.mk
